26:48.594 --> 26:56.626
Every Monday, if you're listening, every Monday at 6.30 on Oakdale Drive in Menlo Park, Mr. Softy is there and he stops by my house.

26:56.930 --> 26:59.414
Uh, so how high in the priority list is like ice cream?

26:59.434 --> 27:05.182
Cause if, if there was a truck, I would just like, you know, I would gladly give volunteer hours to make sure that thing got done.

27:05.202 --> 27:06.063
So yeah.

27:06.083 --> 27:06.223
Yeah.

27:06.243 --> 27:11.972
