27:11.992 --> 27:12.092
Okay.

27:12.452 --> 27:18.501
And we've talked about a lot of times and, um, you know, the healthy people on our staff are like, we can't serve kids ice cream.

27:18.521 --> 27:19.122
And I'm like,

27:20.354 --> 27:21.816
You have to serve kids ice cream.

27:21.836 --> 27:23.980
What are you talking about?

27:24.140 --> 27:29.829
But my wife, who's always the voice of reason, is like, no, you got to couple it with healthy smoothies.

27:29.969 --> 27:34.236
So you give out ice cream, yes, but also you have healthy smoothies.

27:34.276 --> 27:35.678
That's the way you get the vitamins and the kids.

27:36.319 --> 27:39.824
And yeah, I always said the same thing to anyone that's ever interested.

27:40.185 --> 27:40.946
If you build it,

27:41.858 --> 27:42.579
I will run it.

27:45.483 --> 27:46.004
I will run it.

27:46.024 --> 27:47.887
I will figure a way to run it.

27:47.947 --> 27:49.829
That would be so well received.

27:50.390 --> 27:51.071
So easily.

27:51.572 --> 27:52.954
Maybe Mr. Softy, if you're listening.

27:53.194 --> 27:53.635
Yes.

27:53.655 --> 27:54.756
If you've got a truck you're not using.

27:55.277 --> 27:55.778
