27:55.818 --> 27:57.540
Yeah, yeah, we'd be happy to talk to you.

27:57.921 --> 28:03.128
Well, we're super excited, Christian.

28:03.148 --> 28:03.769
Thank you so much.

28:03.809 --> 28:10.098
I mean, we're excited just around what you're doing constantly and for us to be able to insert one day of, like,

28:10.242 --> 28:12.366
Focused let's partner up together.

28:12.386 --> 28:18.238
We're so happy to do so so again for the Bay 5ks happening on March 18th 28th.

